006B"}, "display_name": "VIRUS NO MORE", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Destroy as viruses as possible that attack you in town \nand send you to the hospital. Use your skill, protect yourself with masks, take the right treatments, confine yourself, avoid super-contaminators etc ... \nAll means are good, from Beijing to Tokyo via Paris and New York and other alpha cities, to survive the virus attack. Enjoy! \ud83e\udda0\ud83d\ude00", "short_description": "A topical Shoot 'Em Up. Are you going to survive the pandemic ?"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "949814135998686", "locale": "es_LA", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "VIRUS NO MORE", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Destruye tantos virus como puedas que te ataquen en la ciudad y te env\u00eden al hospital. Usa tu habilidad, prot\u00e9gete con mascarillas, haz los tratamientos adecuados, conf\u00ednese y evite los supercontaminadores. Todos los medios son buenos de Beijing a Tokio a trav\u00e9s de Par\u00eds y Nueva York y otras ciudades alfa, para sobrevivir en virus. \u00a1Disfruta! \ud83e\udda0\ud83d\ude00", "short_description": "Un Shoot 'Em Up de actualidad. \u00bfSobrevivir\u00e1 al virus ?"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "703753607782392", "locale": "ja_JP", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "VIRUS NO MORE", "keywords": [], "long_description": "\u8a71\u984c\u306e\u30b7\u30e5\u30fc\u30c6\u30a3\u30f3\u30b0\u30b2\u30fc\u30e0 'Em Up\uff01 \u753a\u3067\u3042\u306a\u305f\u3092\u653b\u6483\u3059\u308b\u30a6\u30a4\u30eb\u30b9\u3092\u53ef\u80fd\u306a\u9650\u308a\u7834\u58ca\u3059\u308b\u305d\u3057\u3066\u3042\u306a\u305f\u3092\u75c5\u9662\u306b\u9001\u308a\u307e\u3059\u3002 \u3042\u306a\u305f\u306e\u30b9\u30ad\u30eb\u3092\u4f7f\u3044\u3001\u30de\u30b9\u30af\u3067\u8eab\u3092\u5b88\u308a\u3001\u9069\u5207\u306a\u6cbb\u7642\u3092\u53d7\u3051\u3001\u81ea\u5206\u3092\u9589\u3058\u8fbc\u3081 \u